data.title: Dodge County Schools School District at Eastman,Dodge County, Georgia
data.meta_description: Dodge County Schools school district(PK - 12) is located at 720 College St Eastman, GA 31023. Its phone number is 478-374-3783. The district had 215 teachers: 115 elementary school teachers and 75 secondary school teachers.Dodge County Schools had 3401 students: 467 in special education program, 51 in English Language Learner(EEL) program.
